	@GetMapping(&quot;/callable&quot;)
	public Mono&lt;String&gt; callable() throws InterruptedException {
		log.info(&quot;callable&quot;);
		return Mono.fromCallable(() -&gt; {
			log.info(&quot;async&quot;);
			Thread.sleep(2000);
			return &quot;hello&quot;;
		});
	}

As a side note, `Thread.sleep` should never be used within a reactive pipeline in actual application code.

